@node Introduction "Color to Gray: Introduction"

                                  Introduction
                                 --------------

   Color to Gray is a plugin for the famous Image-Manipulation-Program
   ArtEffect2+. As a normal PlugIn it integrates seamlessly in ArtEffect2+'s
   menu and waits happily for your attention.

   Color to Gray does just what its name promises, the color channels can
   be freely weighted.

@endnode

